people who believe this way.

00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:41.330 align:middle line:90%
Well, Stacy has it, but I don't.

00:01:41.330 --> 00:01:43.077 align:middle line:90%
>> We all have it.

00:01:43.077 --> 00:01:43.910 align:middle line:90%
You know what it is?

00:01:43.910 --> 00:01:45.150 align:middle line:90%
It's a technical skill.

00:01:45.150 --> 00:01:49.740 align:middle line:84%
It's a technical skill
that we can all use,

00:01:49.740 --> 00:01:52.020 align:middle line:90%
that's very immediate.

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:55.970 align:middle line:84%
And we can all harness
it to change our lives.

00:01:55.970 --> 00:01:57.050 align:middle line:90%
It's absolutely so easy.

00:01:57.050 --> 00:01:58.430 align:middle line:84%
I think the thing
is that we were all

00:01:58.430 --> 00:01:59.430 align:middle line:90%
