which is not true, absolutely

00:02:05.780 --> 00:02:07.050 align:middle line:90%
not true.

00:02:07.050 --> 00:02:10.039 align:middle line:84%
We're not taught just how to
open up and look within and ask

00:02:10.039 --> 00:02:12.706 align:middle line:84%
