00:16:42.220 --> 00:16:44.320 align:middle line:84%
Yes, it will happen
when it happens.

00:16:44.320 --> 00:16:46.360 align:middle line:84%
And a lot of times,
when clients come to me

00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:51.153 align:middle line:84%
and say, where's my
soulmate, and I'll say,

00:16:51.153 --> 00:16:53.445 align:middle line:84%
you have this great relationship
coming in the next six

00:16:53.445 --> 00:16:56.070 align:middle line:84%
to nine months, and well, let me
describe your soulmate to you,

00:16:56.070 --> 00:16:57.060 align:middle line:84%
and I know you're not
going to like this,

00:16:57.060 --> 00:16:58.270 align:middle line:90%
but he's three years away.

00:16:58.270 --> 00:17:00.320 align:middle line:84%
And they say-- yes,
there's free will,

00:17:00.320 --> 00:17:02.400 align:middle line:84%
and yes, you can make
it happen faster.

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:05.425 align:middle line:84%
But you can also bring to you
an understanding that, OK, well,

00:17:05.425 --> 00:17:07.050 align:middle line:84%
maybe I have things
to learn and things

00:17:07.050 --> 00:17:08.490 align:middle line:84%
to do before my
soulmate gets here so

00:17:08.490 --> 00:17:10.230 align:middle line:84%
let me attract the love
that I need so I can be

00:17:10.230 --> 00:17:11.400 align:middle line:90%
happy and safe and comfortable.

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:13.233 align:middle line:84%
So then all of sudden,
the idea of soulmate,

00:17:13.233 --> 00:17:15.770 align:middle line:84%
that need for soulmate
is not as strong in that

00:17:15.770 --> 00:17:17.579 align:middle line:84%
when you're happy,
and you're busy,

00:17:17.579 --> 00:17:21.569 align:middle line:84%
and you're in the
flow of energy, then--

00:17:21.569 --> 00:17:23.868 align:middle line:84%
so that's the answer to,
do I ask for my soulmate,

00:17:23.868 --> 00:17:25.410 align:middle line:84%
you know, how do I
pray for soulmate.

00:17:25.410 --> 00:17:28.710 align:middle line:84%
>> And we often have,
according to your book--

00:17:28.710 --> 00:17:33.460 align:middle line:84%
I'm paraphrasing, but I think
this is part of your message.

00:17:33.460 --> 00:17:36.570 align:middle line:84%
What we have at the moment
is exactly what we need,

00:17:36.570 --> 00:17:38.010 align:middle line:84%
if we just pay
attention to that.

00:17:38.010 --> 00:17:39.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Absolutely.

00:17:39.780 --> 00:17:45.540 align:middle line:10%
We're all taught then we can't--
that what we want is not what

00:17:45.540 --> 00:17:46.920 align:middle line:10%
we're meant to have.

00:17:46.920 --> 00:17:48.060 align:middle line:10%
We all limit ourselves.

00:17:48.060 --> 00:17:49.988 align:middle line:10%
And we're also
taught that we're not

00:17:49.988 --> 00:17:51.780 align:middle line:10%
supposed to be really
happy in our careers,

00:17:51.780 --> 00:17:53.190 align:middle line:10%
and we're supposed to
do one thing for money

00:17:53.190 --> 00:17:54.500 align:middle line:10%
and one thing for happiness.

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:56.190 align:middle line:10%
And we're all
taught these things.

00:17:56.190 --> 00:17:59.470 align:middle line:10%
And no, what you
want is your destiny.

00:17:59.470 --> 00:18:00.340 align:middle line:10%
Like, that's it.

00:18:00.340 --> 00:18:02.280 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if you feel like you're
supposed go off and be a nurse,

00:18:02.280 --> 00:18:04.620 align:middle line:84%
and be a healer, or be a
writer, or be an actress,

00:18:04.620 --> 00:18:07.110 align:middle line:84%
then if that's what
you want, that's

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:09.427 align:middle line:84%
your higher self, that's
that energy talking to you.

00:18:09.427 --> 00:18:11.260 align:middle line:84%
Like, that's what you're
supposed to go for.

00:18:11.260 --> 00:18:12.210 align:middle line:90%
Like, that's it.

00:18:12.210 --> 00:18:13.740 align:middle line:84%
Like, that's not
just some desire

00:18:13.740 --> 00:18:15.948 align:middle line:84%
that you're supposed to put
in the back of your head,

00:18:15.948 --> 00:18:18.298 align:middle line:84%
while you're miserable
at this 9-to-5 job

00:18:18.298 --> 00:18:19.590 align:middle line:90%
as an administrative assistant.

00:18:19.590 --> 00:18:22.830 align:middle line:84%
So yes, what we want is
what we're supposed to have.

00:18:22.830 --> 00:18:25.530 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the things
you say in your book is,

00:18:25.530 --> 00:18:29.100 align:middle line:84%
the closer you are
to your connection,

00:18:29.100 --> 00:18:30.690 align:middle line:90%
the less you need ritual.

00:18:30.690 --> 00:18:31.680 align:middle line:90%
>> Mm-hmm.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:34.740 align:middle line:84%
The less-- and the easier it
is to manifest what you want.

00:18:34.740 --> 00:18:36.630 align:middle line:90%
>> What does that mean?

00:18:36.630 --> 00:18:39.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Oh, this is the thing I
rejected about those books when

00:18:39.690 --> 00:18:41.130 align:middle line:84%
I was in high
school and studying.

00:18:41.130 --> 00:18:42.600 align:middle line:84%
I picked up some
meditation books.

00:18:42.600 --> 00:18:45.570 align:middle line:84%
And they said, oh, you
have to think this for--

00:18:45.570 --> 00:18:48.240 align:middle line:84%
the process they
had me go through

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:50.490 align:middle line:84%
was this whole 10-step
process before I could even

00:18:50.490 --> 00:18:51.860 align:middle line:90%
get to a meditative state.

00:18:51.860 --> 00:18:53.720 align:middle line:90%
And I said, no, it just--

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:55.797 align:middle line:84%
it takes 10 seconds,
30 seconds, a minute.

00:18:55.797 --> 00:18:56.880 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't take that long.

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:58.892 align:middle line:84%
>> What do you call it,
instant gratification?

00:18:58.892 --> 00:19:00.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Instant gratification
psychic ability,

00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:02.120 align:middle line:90%
instant gratification intuition.

00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:03.490 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:19:03.490 --> 00:19:04.730 align:middle line:90%
>> It really is.

00:19:04.730 --> 00:19:05.910 align:middle line:90%
The closer you live to that.

00:19:05.910 --> 00:19:07.827 align:middle line:84%
Now, I've seen plenty
of people in my lectures

00:19:07.827 --> 00:19:10.020 align:middle line:84%
that are really far
away from getting there.

00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:12.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Because they feel like they
have to sit down and do this,

00:19:12.930 --> 00:19:13.290 align:middle line:90%
and om and--

00:19:13.290 --> 00:19:13.560 align:middle line:90%
>> And you know what?

00:19:13.560 --> 00:19:14.770 align:middle line:84%
And there's nothing
wrong with that.

00:19:14.770 --> 00:19:15.240 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:19:15.240 --> 00:19:15.550 align:middle line:90%
>> Right?

00:19:15.550 --> 00:19:16.540 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:19:16.540 --> 00:19:18.810 align:middle line:84%
>> But if you are in a
car, and you are driving,

00:19:18.810 --> 00:19:21.352 align:middle line:84%
and you're in a mall, and you
need a parking space right now,

00:19:21.352 --> 00:19:24.030 align:middle line:90%
you don't have time for that.

00:19:24.030 --> 00:19:26.310 align:middle line:90%
So it's nice to have the option.

00:19:26.310 --> 00:19:28.770 align:middle line:84%
But the more you get
into this perfect place--

00:19:28.770 --> 00:19:31.325 align:middle line:84%
and we've all had moments
where time has just flown by.

00:19:31.325 --> 00:19:32.700 align:middle line:84%
We've all had
moments where we've

00:19:32.700 --> 00:19:35.580 align:middle line:84%
been with friends, or family,
or with our mates, where

00:19:35.580 --> 00:19:37.890 align:middle line:84%
we felt really great about
ourselves, where we felt

00:19:37.890 --> 00:19:39.307 align:middle line:84%
like everything
is possible, where

00:19:39.307 --> 00:19:44.070 align:middle line:84%
we felt not limited by fear
and by the outside influences.

00:19:44.070 --> 00:19:46.050 align:middle line:84%
And what I teach
people is, you can

00:19:46.050 --> 00:19:47.550 align:middle line:90%
get into that perfect place.

00:19:47.550 --> 00:19:50.550 align:middle line:84%
And you can not only get
into it for fleeting moments,

00:19:50.550 --> 00:19:53.400 align:middle line:84%
but you can make it
happen all the time.

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:57.270 align:middle line:84%
And that's what I mean by you
don't need ritual to get there.

00:19:57.270 --> 00:20:01.650 align:middle line:84%
And the more you let this
energy into your life,

00:20:01.650 --> 00:20:03.330 align:middle line:84%
there's like a
little place there.

00:20:03.330 --> 00:20:04.380 align:middle line:90%
Maybe it's in your heart.

00:20:04.380 --> 00:20:06.172 align:middle line:84%
And it grows and grows
and grows and grows.

00:20:06.172 --> 00:20:08.250 align:middle line:84%
So you can actually get
into this perfect place.

00:20:08.250 --> 00:20:11.370 align:middle line:84%
And you can be sitting in
traffic in this perfect place

00:20:11.370 --> 00:20:13.800 align:middle line:84%
or standing on this crowded
bus in this perfect place.

00:20:13.800 --> 00:20:15.358 align:middle line:90%
And also, nothing bothers you.

00:20:15.358 --> 00:20:17.400 align:middle line:84%
All of a sudden, you know
everything is possible.

00:20:17.400 --> 00:20:19.873 align:middle line:84%
So it's those fleeting
moments that you can get

00:20:19.873 --> 00:20:21.040 align:middle line:90%
them to happen all the time.

00:20:21.040 --> 00:20:23.460 align:middle line:84%
And there's no ritual that's
necessary at that point

00:20:23.460 --> 00:20:25.907 align:middle line:84%
in order to get into
this deep state.

00:20:25.907 --> 00:20:27.240 align:middle line:90%
All's you have to do is open up.

00:20:27.240 --> 00:20:29.233 align:middle line:90%
>> So you don't need ceremony.

00:20:29.233 --> 00:20:30.150 align:middle line:90%
You can just go there.

