00:20:38.220 --> 00:20:40.020 align:middle line:84%
What do you find
in the people here?

00:20:40.020 --> 00:20:40.890 align:middle line:90%
What draws you here?

00:20:40.890 --> 00:20:43.320 align:middle line:84%
>> I love doing the Whole
Life Expo, I have to say.

00:20:43.320 --> 00:20:47.370 align:middle line:10%
