this zap of energy

00:20:53.652 --> 00:20:55.860 align:middle line:10%
that you get when you just
sort of come to this place

00:20:55.860 --> 00:20:58.110 align:middle line:10%
where there's a group of
like-minded souls doing this.

00:20:58.110 --> 00:21:01.380 align:middle line:84%
But I really feel like
it's really important to me

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:03.505 align:middle line:84%
to be very closely connected
with the people that

00:21:03.505 --> 00:21:05.130 align:middle line:84%
