00:21:06.390 --> 00:21:07.560 align:middle line:90%
Because I feel like--

00:21:07.560 --> 00:21:09.720 align:middle line:84%
I always remind myself,
like, without them, I

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:12.330 align:middle line:90%
