00:21:12.330 --> 00:21:14.250 align:middle line:84%
Without those people
sitting in the lecture,

00:21:14.250 --> 00:21:15.510 align:middle line:84%
without those people
that come to readings,

00:21:15.510 --> 00:21:16.660 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't be able
to do what I do.

00:21:16.660 --> 00:21:18.690 align:middle line:84%
And I think so often,
healers forget that.

00:21:18.690 --> 00:21:22.690 align:middle line:84%
>> What is the feeling you
get when you end a lecture

00:21:22.690 --> 00:21:24.820 align:middle line:84%
