And it's very contagious.

00:21:55.490 --> 00:21:56.290 align:middle line:90%
>> It is.

00:21:56.290 --> 00:21:56.590 align:middle line:90%
>> You've captured--

00:21:56.590 --> 00:21:57.190 align:middle line:90%
>> It's great.

00:21:57.190 --> 00:21:58.160 align:middle line:90%
>> You've captured this room.

